column5: I never grew up I just bought bigger toys  Now I want to see a video of you driving it.  It looks great man I made a chopper when I was 12 yrs old.

I know the guy who built the bike in the vid (well kinda know - he's married to a family friend).  In fact I went to the school he's riding at from kindergarten to grade 8.  He holds a guiness record for tallest bike (or did) and has a couple books out about doing custom bikes.
Nice!! How much do these toys go for anyway??  Daniel
